{
  "stem": "4695.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was thinking, OK, I cannot go now back on the front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Maybe they will give me free to go to see my wife.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I haven't seen her so long-- three years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I talked with the doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The doctor said, you know, you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] the manager from the hospital is also a Jewish woman, Maria Mazevna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You talk it over with Maria Mazevna, and maybe you will go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then I talk over Maria Mazevna, she looked at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She started talking a little bit Jewish to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[YIDDISH], she say-- she tell me to listen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I will   not answer you, Ignac.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I give you five minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I go out, you have papers filling on the top drawer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Open the drawer in five minutes and look at what is written.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I opened the door to see what is written in Russian-- to take good care of me, and they need me on the front.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And soon when I can go, even to supply room with a doctor and to bring me back to the battalion, with a doctor if I need.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They need me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this after Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This a little bit-- a year later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was already, you see, in-- And so was it-- when she comes back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, OK, I know she can nothing do, because she had the order, with the talking, because when she will show me she can be go to jail herself, and not talking-- good friends.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We said goodbye to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I was still on the-- Meantime, I was back to my battalion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at once, we take a high ranking German officer, you see, and several prisoners.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We attacked them, and we took them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I was supposed to question him.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
